```

```
id:               chaos_theory
name:             Chaos Theory
domain:           math_physical
decade:           1970s
prominence:       major
field_type:       foundational
period_active:    1963–present
key_concepts:     Sensitive dependence, strange attractors, Lorenz attractor, period doubling
tags:             dynamics, nonlinear
notes:            Lorenz (1963), May (1976), Feigenbaum universality; popularized by Gleick (1987)
```

```
id:               fractal_geometry
name:             Fractal Geometry
domain:           math_physical
decade:           1980s
prominence:       major
field_type:       foundational
period_active:    1975–present
key_concepts:     Self-similarity, fractal dimension, power laws, scale invariance
tags:             mathematics, geometry
notes:            Mandelbrot's fractal geometry of nature; ubiquitous scaling in complex systems
```

```
