period_active:    1998–present
key_concepts:     Small-world networks, scale-free topology, hubs, preferential attachment, community structure
tags:             core, computational
notes:            Watts & Strogatz (1998), Barabási & Albert (1999); transformed understanding of complex structure
```

```
